00:00:05,500 --> 00:00:12,500
Transcript and translation
from April Fisher http://youtu.be/vx-SCOBktzc
Sung by Sia Koskina (Σία Κοσκινά)

00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:17,000
The snow glows white on the mountain tonight,
Το χιόνι αγκαλιάζει το βουνό
To chióni agkaliázei to voynó
The snow embraces the mountain

00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:20,000
not a footprint to be seen
Δίχως ίχνη, δίχως φωνή
Díchōs íchnī, díchōs fōnī́
Without a trace, without a voice

00:00:20,500 --> 00:00:23,500
A kingdom of isolation,
Βασίλισσα σ῾ ένα θρόνο
Vasílissa sh éna thróno
Queen in a throne

00:00:23,500 --> 00:00:27,000
and it looks like I'm the queen
από πάγο και σιωπή
apó págo kai siōpī́
of ice and silence

00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:34,000
The wind is howling like this swirling storm inside
Είναι η σιωπή π῾ ουρλιάζει πόνο αναζητά
Eínai ī siōpī́ ph oyrliázei póno anazītá
It's the silence that's screaming, looking for pain

00:00:34,500 --> 00:00:41,000
Couldn't keep it in, heaven knows I tried
Πώς να κρατηθεί μέσα μου βαθειά?
Pṓs na kratītheí mésa moy vatheiá?
How can it be kept deep inside of me?

00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:46,000
Don't let them in, don't let them see
Κανείς να μην υποψιαστεί
Kaneís na mīn ypopsiasteí
No one must suspect

00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:49,500
Be the good girl you always had to be
Θα ῾μαι η καλή που ξέρουν μια ζωή
Tha hmai ī kalī́ poy xéroyn mia zōī́
I'll be the good one they've known all their lives

00:00:49,500 --> 00:00:54,000
Conceal, don't feel, don't let them know
Να μη χαθει το μυστικό...!
Na mī chathei to mystikó...!
The secret must not get lost...!

00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:58,000
Well, now they know!
Μα είναι γνωστό!
Ma eínai gnōstó!
But (now) it's known!

00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:02,000
Let it go, let it go!
Και ξεχνώ, τα ξεχνώ
Kai xechnṓ, ta xechnṓ
And I forget, I forget

00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:06,000
Can't hold it back any more!
Και πίςω δεν κοιτώ
Kai písō den koitṓ
And I'm not looking back

00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:09,500
Let it go, let it go!
Τα ξεχνώ, προχωρώ
Ta xechnṓ, prochōrṓ
I forget, I move on

00:01:09,500 --> 00:01:13,000
Turn away and slam the door!
Τη ζωή μου ξεκινώ!
Tī zōī́ moy xekinṓ!
I start my life!

00:01:13,500 --> 00:01:19,500
I don't care what they're going to say
Φτάνει πια! Κό βω σκοινί!
Ftánei pia! Kó vō skoiní!
That's enough! I cut the cord!

00:01:19,500 --> 00:01:24,000
Let the storm rage on
Κι ας παγώνει η γη...
Ki as pagṓnei ī gī...
And let the earth freeze...

00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:27,000
The cold never bothered me anyway.
Το κρύο την καρδιά μου δεν τηυ ενοχλεί.
To krýo tīn kardiá moy den tīy enochleí.
The cold doesn't bother my heart.

00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:33,500
It's funny how some distance
Ετην απεραντοδύνη,
Etīn aperantodýnī,
In the infinity,

00:01:33,500 --> 00:01:37,000
Makes everything seem small
όλα φαίνονται μικρά
óla faínontai mikrá
everything seems small

00:01:37,500 --> 00:01:41,000
And the fears that once controlled me
Τωρα οι φόβοι κι οι ενοχές μου
Tōra oi fóvoi ki oi enochés moy
Now my fears and my guilt

00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:45,000
Can't get to me at all!
δε μ῾ εξουσιάζουν πια!
de mh exoysiázoyn pia!
don't control me any more!

00:01:45,500 --> 00:01:49,000
It's time to see what I can do
Καιρός να μάθω τι μπορώ!
Kairós na máthō ti mporṓ!
It's time to find out what I can do!

00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:52,500
To test the limits and break through
Τα όριά μου εγώ τα ξεπερνώ!
Ta óriá moy egṓ ta xepernṓ!
I surpass my limits!

00:01:52,500 --> 00:01:56,500
No right, no wrong, no rules for me
Αν βγω απ῾ αυτή τη φυλακή...
An vgō aph aytī́ tī fylakī́...
If I escape from this prison...

00:01:56,500 --> 00:01:59,500
I'm free!
Μου αρκεί...!
Moy arkeí...!
That's enough for me!

00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:03,500
Let it go, let it go!
Και ξεχνώ, τα ξεχνώ
Kai xechnṓ, ta xechnṓ
And I forget, I forget

00:02:03,500 --> 00:02:07,500
I am one with the wind and sky
Γίνομαι ένα με τον ουρανό
Gínomai éna me ton oyranó
I become one with the sky

00:02:07,500 --> 00:02:11,000
Let it go, let it go!
Και ξεχνώ, τα ξεχνώ
Kai xechnṓ, ta xechnṓ
And I forget, I forget

00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:15,000
You'll never see me cry
Το δάκρυ συγκρατώ!
To dákry sygkratṓ!
I hold back my tears!

00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:21,500
Here I stand, and here I'll stay,
Ελεύθερη!
Eleýtherī!
(I am) free!

00:02:21,500 --> 00:02:25,000
Let the storm rage on...
Ας παγώσει η γη...
As pagṓsei ī gī...
Let the earth freeze...

00:02:32,500 --> 00:02:39,000
My power flurries through the air and to the ground
Η δύναμή μου σκίζει πέφτοντας τη γη...
Ī dýnamī́ moy skízei péftontas tī gī...
My power splits the earth as it falls...

00:02:39,500 --> 00:02:46,000
My soul is spiralling in frozen fractals all around
Ψυχή που αναβλύζει σα γλυκού νερού πηγή...
Psychī́ poy anavlýzei sa glykoý neroý pīgī́...
A soul that's streaming like a freshwater spring...

00:02:46,500 --> 00:02:53,000
And one thought crystallizes like an icy blast
Σαν έκρηξη μια σκέψη λιώνει τα βουνά!
San ékrīxī mia sképsī liṓnei ta voyná!
Like an explosion, a thought melts the mountains!

00:02:53,500 --> 00:02:56,500
I'm never going back
Θολό μου παρελθόν
Tholó moy parelthón
My blurry past

00:02:56,500 --> 00:03:00,500
The past is in the past!
Τα λέμε, άντε γεια!
Ta léme, ánte geia!
(See you) Later, goodbye!

00:03:01,500 --> 00:03:04,500
Let it go, let it go!
Και ξεχνώ! Και ξεχνώ!
Kai xechnṓ! Kai xechnṓ!
And I forget! And I forget!

00:03:04,500 --> 00:03:08,500
And I'll rise like the break of dawn
Στα παλιά πίσω δε γυρνώ!
Sta paliá písō de gyrnṓ!
I'm not going back!

00:03:08,500 --> 00:03:12,000
Let it go, let it go!
Τα ξεχνω! Χαιρετώ...
Ta xechnō! Chairetṓ...
I forget! I greet...

00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:15,500
That perfect girl is gone
... το νέο μου εαυτό!
... to néo moy eaytó!
... my new self!

00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:24,500
Here I stand in the light of day
Ζωντανή! Σαν ανατολή!
Zōntanī́! San anatolī́!
(I'm) alive! Like the break of dawn!

00:03:24,500 --> 00:03:30,000
Let the storm rage on!
ΚΙ ΑΣ ΠΑΓΏΣΕΙ Η ΓΗ!
KI AS PAGṒSEI Ī GĪ!
AND LET THE EARTH FREEZE!

